        public boolean registerItemToBuild​(Module module,
                                   java.lang.Object item)
        Registers a command to the manager. The command can be any object. It will be built by the CommandBuilder.
        Parameters:
        module - The module that is registering the command.
        item - The command to register.
        Returns:
        True if the command was registered, false otherwise.
